    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable ride that's been so good to me over the years. It\u2019s in great shape and totally ready for its next adventure! It runs super smoothly and has been well-loved and maintained, so you can just hop in and head out. It's been perfect for my daily commutes and the occasional weekend road trip. I'm really going to miss this one, but it's time for it to find a new home. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
