    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points and a recent valve adjustment to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry that provides communicative feedback and neutral handling characteristics. While showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity make this an ideal candidate for the spirited purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
